{"word":"προσχαρίζομαι","slug":"προσχαρίζομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προσχαρίζομαι</b></el> <p/><a href='S:Deponent Verb, i.e. a Verb of Middle or Passive form with Active sense'>Dep.</a> <i>to gratify</i> or <i>satisfy besides</i>, <el>τινί</el> <b><a href='S:Xenophon'>Xen.</a></b>; <el>τινί τι</el> <i>to give freely besides</i>, <b><a href='S:Strabo'>Strab.</a></b><p/>"}]}